1.title: Clip: A Hero Awakens

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

1.plot: We kick off our play-through of Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild on the Nintendo Switch. After 100 years, the Hero of Time rises from The Tomb of Resurrection to a big bad guy trying to take over. Let's get settled in and play a game that's over five years in the making.

2.title: Clip: The Great Towers Rise

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

2.plot: We continue our way through Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild. A bunch of these ancient towers rise from the ground and I assume it has to do with something with the plot. So tune into this episode and let's find out together.

3.title: Clip: The Oman Au Shrine

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

3.plot: Brian gets through even more shrines and epic adventures in Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild. Join us for even more Zelda and awesome Nintendo Switch coverage on Level-N.

4.title: Clip: The Ja Baij Shrine

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

4.plot: We conquer the Ja Baig shrine, get a new ability, and encounter our first Guardian. Thank goodness it can't come running after us - That would be terrifying.

5.title: Clip: On the Wild Hunt

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

5.plot: Let's hunt ourselves some good meat. Maybe we can finally cook something good to get that cloak we so desperately need.

6.title: Clip: A Story 100 Years in the Making Unfolds

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

6.plot: The destiny of the Hero of Time has been told once again. I'm very happy you don't have to play the other games to realize what's going on - Otherwise I'd be totally out of it.

7.title: Clip: Let the Wind Guide Us!

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

7.plot: Now that we have our handy dandy power sail, we can ride the wind all we want (so long as we have enough stamina). Join Brian for even more Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild on the Nintendo Switch.

8.title: Clip: Tedious Towers are Electrifying

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

8.plot: It's electrifying. After bracing multiple strikes of lightning, we find ourselves another tower. You would think that'd attract more lightning, but I guess not in Hyrule. Join us for even more Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild on the Nintendo Switch.

9.title: Clip: The Tunic is Mine, but Success isn't..

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

9.plot: Okay - So I may or may not have already played a lot of the game off camera - but I couldn't help myself. I'm sorry. It's just - such a good game. You can't blame me for it. Now that we have this stupid tunic, we can climb (most) mountains with ease in Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild.

10.title: Clip: A Pony's Journey to Find Impa!

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

10.plot: He, she, we, wumbo. With the help of our newly acquired steed Wumbo, we go on the search to find Impa.

11.title: Clip: The Legends have a Divine Secret

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

11.plot: In this episode of Breath of the Wild, we head to our (not so much) first Divine Beast. The giant camel will be of great use to our journey to defeat Ganon.

12.title: Clip: Activating the Last Tower

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

12.plot: We finally unlock the complete map. Now we can explore every nook and cranny of Hyrule with the power of teleportation.

13.title: Clip: Blue Fire and a Sheikah Slate Update

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

13.plot: Our in-game Nintendo Switch tablet gets a software update in this episode of BOTW. Hopefully it doesn't slow down our operating system like those pesky Apple updates do.

14.title: Clip: Giant Fairies and a Clothing Upgrade

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

14.plot: That's one big fairy. For just a small fee, we can finally upgrade our clothes. Join Brian as he plays more Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild on the Nintendo Switch.

15.title: Clip: Welcome to Rito Village!

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

15.plot: Next stop, Rito village. Maybe they can help us get to that fancy flying Divine Beast - But not before we solve a shrine and tour the town.

16.title: Clip: Divine Beast Medoh, Part 1

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

16.plot: We get going on our first Divine Beast, Medoh. Will this giant bird be a giant pain in the feathers, or be relatively easy? Find out in today's episode of Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild.

17.title: Clip: Divine Beast Medoh, Part 2

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

17.plot: Medoh is conquered. With the help of our Rito friends, we get one step closer to defeating Ganon.

18.title: Clip: Welcome to the Dolphin Kingdom

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

18.plot: We finally encounter the Zora. Let's find out how to get inside that big old ancient elephant and conquer it's super divine powers.

19.title: Clip: Swimming to the Lynel King

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

19.plot: After not realizing after so long that I can swim up waterfalls, I evade the Lynel and get some arrows.

20.title: Clip: Divine Beast Vah Ruta

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

20.plot: Ruta is next on the platter for a butt kicking. This big ancient elephant is no match for our powers and awesome new flying ability.

21.title: Clip: Master of the Lost Woods

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

21.plot: Knowing exactly how to navigate The Lost Woods, we pull the legendary Master Sword from its' resting place. Thankfully we have enough hearts to pull it without any issue at all!

22.title: Clip: Let's Go Guardian Hunting

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

22.plot: Now that we're super over-powered, we can smash these Guardians with ease. This Master Sword is mighty powerful.

23.title: Clip: Looking Fabulous as Ever

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

23.plot: Next stop, the Gerudo. Although it took a very drastic wardrobe change, we can get in no problem. Link doesn't look all that bad either.

24.title: Clip: Yiga Clan's Mighty Banana's

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

24.plot: What is it with these guys and bananas? I mean I get that they're good - But they're going a little overboard. Let's invade the Yiga clan as stealthily as we can.

25.title: Clip: Divine Beast Naboris, Part 1

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

25.plot: After acquiring the Thunder Helm, we're more than ready to overtake the sandy electric camel. I didn't think these Divine Beasts could get any weirder, but I guess I'm wrong.

26.title: Clip: Divine Beast Naboris, Part 2

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

26.plot: With Divine Beast Naboris out of the way, we can finally use the heat resistance stuff and go to the Goron City. At least that's what we hope for, right?

27.title: Clip: Amiibo and the Goron City

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

27.plot: Shiny Amiibo are shiny. Let me show you my new toys and the proper way to get to Goron City in this episode of Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild.

28.title: Clip: Saving Yunobo

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

28.plot: The scrawny descendant of the Goron that helped Link over 100 years ago needs our help. I guess it's our obligation to help him since it's part of the story.

29.title: Clip: Boulder Canons Burn Baby Burn

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

29.plot: Let's launch this ball of power at a giant lizard on the side of a volcano. I didn't think Zelda could get any weirder, but it never fails to prove me wrong.

30.title: Clip: Divine Beast Vah Rudania, Part 1

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

30.plot: Welcome to Divine Beast Vah Rudania. This Lizard doesn't stand a chance. That is, if we can take the heat.

31.title: Clip: Divine Beast Vah Rudania, Part 2

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

31.plot: Divine Beast Vah Rudania turns out to be more complicated than I would've liked due to flames engulfing me. Now that it's conquered once and for all, we can leave this dreaded flame basin forever.

32.title: Clip: Finding Fairies and Sidequests!

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

32.plot: We are getting close to the end...but we do has some side questing to take care of first.

33.title: Clip: The Twelve Memories

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

33.plot: Let's recapture some of the most influential moments of Link's past. Join Brian as he finds a total of 13 memories that will ultimately unlock the true ending to Breath of the Wild.

34.title: Clip: We Found Kilton

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

34.plot: At long last. We found this weird looking, hunchback salesman in the wild. Now we can score some seriously awesome gear that we can only find through him. We're just about done with Breath of the Wild.

35.title: Clip: The Grand Finale

episode of.title: Clip: Legend of Zelda Breath of the Wild Playthrough (TV Series 2017– )

35.plot: The Grand Finale is here. After one failed recording, we conquer Calamity Ganon and restore peace to Hyrule once and for all. It's been an absolute pleasure to play through this masterpiece of a game for you fantastic people.

imdb.plot outline: Brian plays through the very highly anticipated Legend of Zelda breath of the Wild. Using the powers of the Nintendo Switch and the mighty Pro controller, we'll explore, conquer, and die repeatedly in the open-world goodness of Hyrule Kingdom. Let's defeat Calamity Ganon together.
